Fortune Financial Group Inc saidit extended its stock repurchase program for an additional sixmonths.    The program, which began last April, will extend to April16, 1988, the company said.    Last April the board authorized the repurchase of up to400,000 common shares, of which 111,200 were repurchased, thecompany said.    The company said it may purchase another 288,800 shares inthe open market.    Reuter&#3;